data.description: Modern Living at Its Best! This Park West home features an open floor plan, four bedrooms, two bath and three car garage. Charming kitchen with granite countertops, Island, and pantry. Master bedroom with walk-in closet and shower. Beautiful backyard landscaped with artificial grass, built-in bench, and extended covered patio. Double gate side access. Leased solar panels to save on your electricity bill. Call today to schedule your viewing!
